data.description: Calling all investors. Here's the perfect home to add to your rental inventory or fix and flip. ARV range $235-$275+. Needs mostly cosmetics. Beautiful split level home with open floor plan, large kitchen, sunny separate dining room, spacious living room with fireplace, huge master suite, laminate floors and private back yard. Super convenient location, in a quiet suburban neighborhood, close to Arabia Mountain Park/Nature Center and Panola Mountain State Park. Don't miss this one.
